summary: An ordinance relating to the acquisition by condemnation of certain Lots in Blocks 432, 433, 439, 440, 441 and 442, Seattle Tide Lands; in Blocks 432A, 433A, 439A, 440A, 441A and 442A, Haller's Supplemental Plat of Blocks 428, 433, 439, 440, 441 and 442, Seattle Tide Lands; in Tracts "B", "D", "E" and "F", Prospect Tracts; and in Section 12, Township 24 North, Range 3 East, W. M. for corporate uses including sanitary fill; and providing for payment from the Emergency Fund.
